  "prompt": "Which Harry Potter character was worst portrayed in the movies?",
  "response": "Opinions on which Harry Potter character was worst portrayed in the movies can vary among fans, but a commonly cited character is Ginny Weasley. Many fans feel that her character lacks depth and development in the films compared to her portrayal in the books, where she is depicted as strong, independent, and pivotal to the story. \n\nAnother frequently mentioned character is Moaning Myrtle, whose portrayal some fans felt leaned too heavily into a comedic interpretation, overshadowing her more tragic backstory in the books. \n\nUltimately, it often depends on individual preferences and attachments to the source material, so different fans may have varying opinions on which character was not done justice in the adaptations.",
